{"body": "I don't think we should change `Rails` to `Ruby` but we should change `Test::Unit` to `Minitest`.\r\n\r\nRails actually ships with a lot of testing Components specifically for Minitest. All the glue is provided, which is why Rails ships with `Minitest` and not with `Rspec`. To use rspec the same way you need `rspec-rails`, which is not part of Rails itself.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/23318968", "created_at": "2013-08-27T08:00:22Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/12033#issuecomment-23318968", "updated_at": "2013-08-27T08:00:22Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 12033, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/senny/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/senny/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/senny/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/senny", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/senny/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/senny", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/senny/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/3d698e2872c07061a455d9e250861235?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Fd1359f9934ee5a75ed441ffce412a0a1.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/senny/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/senny/received_events", "gravatar_id": "3d698e2872c07061a455d9e250861235", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/senny/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "senny", "type": "User", "id": 5402, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/senny/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "523aaf49bd3543c151018e59"}, "id": 23318968, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/12033"}
